  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Attention to detail is in every part of the Montana Lodge &amp; Spa Hotel, from their first-class service to incredible food and wellness facilities. The boutique hotel has been designed with the mountains in mind, using local materials and art.</span></p>
<h2><span>Five Star Service</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel has more than earned its five star rating. Personal service is at the core of everything they do and a friendly welcome is something you can expect here. A free shuttle runs to and from the ski lifts every day from 8:30am to 5:30pm.</span></p>
<p><span>The hotel is available on Bed &amp; Breakfast with a refined international buffet to start your day off right. If</span> you fancy staying in for dinner, there are two wonderful A La Carte restaurants on site serving fine quality dishes, the Bistro Alpino and Ottavio's Lounge. If you want to try something different, head into La Thuile to explore what's on offer.</p>
<h2>Relaxation</h2>
<p>You won't find better spa facilities in La Thuile than at the Montana Lodge &amp; Spa. The heated indoor pool overlooks Mount Ruitor so you can enjoy incredible views while you relax. After a long day on the slopes you can unwind in the outdoor hot tub, Turkish bath, vitarium or sauna.</p>]]></description>
